{"tid":337911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"操普通話4歲男童被遺棄落馬洲管制站","createTime":"2017-07-27T17:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T05:49:22.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6dda9150ee7b4294da7034900f2d9f2d6982a8b","tid":337911,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:02:33.000Z","msg":"昨午2時，落馬洲支線管制站，一名年約4至5歲姓廖男童獨自徘徊，職員發現報警。警員接報到場，將他送往北區醫院檢查。案件暫列對所看管兒童或少年人虐待或忽略，交邊界警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n男童操普通話，身高約1米，瘦身材，圓面型，被發現時身穿一套白色長袖上衣、白色長褲及藍色拖鞋。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲任何就案件有資料提供的市民，盡快與任何一間警署聯絡，或致電3661 4400或3661 4052與調查人員聯絡。"},{"pid":"aa8398255c61560c921c9ee4b84eab4d2791aed4","tid":337911,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:02:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57010903&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57010903%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170728&d=5f8aTq4Pbr%2B9gATaFqyk6MmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=6330c32b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57010903%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170728&h=7177a2a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57010903&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170728</a>"},{"pid":"1a839aa149c91233d0c1f90bc5cd4b00ee6505d4","tid":337911,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"香港人又要納稅幫支那狗養便宜仔"},{"pid":"b388267a308933d583e49e2f4fd8958690cbdc21","tid":337911,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"又掉落黎叫香港人養佢？"},{"pid":"4a0b543d04eec4011ec36f90e6c58fd91325eb9e","tid":337911,"uid":58250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"遲啲個乜柒膠鐵實會有勁多呢啲<i